<div id="review_2847342420" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2847342420" />
    <a title="David Kettlewood" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/98167426-david-kettlewood"><img alt="David Kettlewood" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2847342420?book_show_action=true">Jun 27, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="David Kettlewood" class="user" itemprop="url" name="David Kettlewood" href="/user/show/98167426-david-kettlewood">David Kettlewood</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/13035338-gettysburg--the-first-day">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2847342420" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16387747687550354149"><strong>Great, detailed account of Day 1</strong><br/><br/>This is the first Day 1 only account that I’ve read. I thoroughly enjoyed the research and the use of great sources. Has me even more interested to read his Day 2 account as I hear that’s his best work. I’ve thoroughly enjoyed this one!</span>

