            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2060057-shelly?shelf=civil-war">civil-war</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2060057-shelly?shelf=year-2013">year-2013</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2060057-shelly?shelf=nf-history-civl-war">nf-history-civl-war</a>, 
